visual_description.name: outdoor_string_light_party_setting.jpg
visual_description.description: Covered outdoor seating area, string lights, dim lighting, tables with chairs, centerpiece with flowers and pumpkins. Slightly dark. Warm orange-brown tones.
visual_description.score_basis: Dimly lit, which creates a cozy mood, but details are hard to see. The composition is symmetrical with a pleasing arrangement, but image resolution is mediocre. Lights add warmth; overall environment feels inviting but lacks sharpness and clarity.
